Package ke.go.moh.oec

Interface Summary
IService This interface is used for passing data requests and responses between the OpenEMRConnect (OEC) library and software using that library.
 

Class Summary
ClinicalDocument Representation of a HL7/ASTM Clinical Care Document (CCD).
Fingerprint A recorded fingerprint, used as a method of identifying a person.
LogEntry Describe a log entry.
Person Describe a person with respect to a person index.
PersonIdentifier An identifier that has been assigned to a person by one of the systems using OpenEMRConnect.
PersonRequest Data that is supplied as part of a request for person information.
PersonResponse Data that is returned in response to a request for person information.
RelatedPerson Describe a person who is related to a given person.
RequestTypeId Define data request type IDs for the getData() method of the IService interface.
Visit Record of a visit of a patient to a health care facility.
